{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 9421,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "すぐに服を着替えて飛び出す。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I quickly changed my clothes and dashed out."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9422,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、ウスピラ将軍！？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, General Uspira?!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9423,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "廊下で、ウスピラに近侍する少女兵が",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "In the hallway, a young female soldier who serves Uspira"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9424,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "飛び出してきた上官に目を丸くした。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "widely opened her eyes at the officer who suddenly rushed out."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9425,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今、どうなっているの。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What is happening right now?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9426,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　昨日何があったか、知っている者は……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Does anyone know what happened yesterday...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9427,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、は、はい……昨日は、サイアス将軍がいらして",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, y-yes... Yesterday, General Saias came"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9428,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ウスピラ将軍をお連れしていて……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and escorted General Uspira...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9429,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「サイアスが……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Saias...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9430,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「は、はい。ウスピラ将軍が酔い潰れたから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-yes. Because General Uspira was completely drunk,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9431,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　少し寝かせてあげて欲しいと……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "he wanted to have her rest a little..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9432,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今日は休暇になった、って……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so today was made a day off...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9433,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「信じたの、そんな話……！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You believed such a story...!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9434,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「えっ、ち、違うんですか……？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eh, i-is that not true...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9435,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　サイアス将軍が仰るから、ええと、その……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Since General Saias said so, um, well...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9436,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ".............."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9437,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "少女兵は顔を赤くして言い淀んだ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The young female soldier blushed and hesitated to speak."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9438,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "おおかた、サイアスが紳士的に、平然と、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Most likely, Saias had calmly and gentlemanly deceived the girl."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9439,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "少女を騙したのだろう。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He probably tricked the girl."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9440,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、で、ですからサイアス将軍は何もしてません。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"So, th-that's why General Saias did nothing wrong."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9441,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　着替えとかは、私が」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I helped with changing clothes, for example.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9442,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………そう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...I see.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9443,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "懸命にサイアスの潔白を主張する少女に、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "To the girl who earnestly insisted on Saias's innocence,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9444,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ウスピラは何かを言う気をなくした。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Uspira lost the will to say anything."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9445,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "（それにしても、いったい何がしたくて……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(Still, what on earth did he want to do...?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9446,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そもそも、サイアスはどこ……？）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "And where is Saias in the first place...?)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9447,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "なぜだか、嫌な予感がしていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "For some reason, I had a bad feeling."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9448,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "両親に先立たれ、自分だけが生き残り……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Having lost both parents, I was the only one left alive..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9449,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "意識を取り戻して、その姿を捜した時の記憶が、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The memory of regaining consciousness and searching for that figure"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9450,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "いやにはっきりと脳裏に浮かんでくる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "came vividly to mind."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9451,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ウスピラ将軍！　そちらでしたか！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"General Uspira! So you were over there!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9452,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　休暇の時に申し訳ございません！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Sorry to bother you during your leave!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9453,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "小走りで、ウスピラの部下がやって来た。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "At a brisk pace, Uspira's subordinate came over."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9454,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それはいいわ。何？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That's fine. What is it?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9455,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　サイアスは……炎軍はどうしているの？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "How are Saias and the Flame Army doing?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9456,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「炎軍は、本日氷軍の代わりに防衛を担当すると。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The Flame Army is in charge of defense today instead of the Ice Army."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9457,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そして先ほど、大規模な残党が防衛線の内側に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "And just a moment ago, a large group of remnants were"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9458,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　集結しつつあるとの情報で、炎軍は出撃しました」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "reported gathering inside the defensive line, so the Flame Army has deployed.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9459,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……………！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...........!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9460,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ですが、センサー地蔵を経由して確認したところ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"However, after checking via the Sensor Jizo,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9461,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　予想していたよりも数が多いようです！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "it seems their numbers are higher than expected!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9462,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「すぐに防衛隊を……二小隊残して出撃準備。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Immediately prepare for deployment, leaving two squads for defense."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9463,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　……急いで」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "...Hurry.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9464,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「は、ははっ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-yes sir!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9465,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "氷軍は、すぐさま準備を整えて出撃した。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The Ice Army quickly prepared and departed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9466,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "…………",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "........"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9467,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9468,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「どういうつもりか。聞いてもいい？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What were you thinking? Can I ask?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9469,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "氷軍の援護によって、魔軍の撃退には成功した。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "With the support of the Ice Army, they succeeded in repelling the demon army."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9470,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "その場で、サイアスはウスピラに詰め寄られていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "At that scene, Saias was confronted by Uspira."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9471,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ムチャは自分の専売特許、って？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You say reckless acts are your exclusive specialty?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9472,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふざけるのはやめて」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Stop joking.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9473,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ぴしゃりと言われて、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Being snapped at sharply,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9474,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "サイアスは苦笑しながら少し顎を撫でた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saias gave a wry smile and scratched his chin a bit."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9475,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……ウスピラが、相変わらず",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Uspira, as always,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9476,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　無理を止めてくれないんでね。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "won't let me overexert myself."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9477,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ちょっと出しゃばってみた」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "So I tried to take the initiative a little.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9478,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ".............."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9479,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「君に休養が必要と感じたのも、本当だ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It's true that I felt you needed rest."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9480,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今、倒れられでもしたら、ゼスも傾くし俺も困る」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If you collapsed now, Zeth would falter and I would be troubled."
    }
  ]
}

